TDI-CLOSING-CD expansion [(TIF-32) COND-CLOSING-CD of LAST-PERIOD-SATISFIED-GROUP and (TIF-50) TDI-CLOSING-CD OF BASIC-TAX-MOD-REC] from 2 positions to 3 positions.
IRM 2.3.26, dated January 1, 2011, is superseded.
Table of
2.3.26.1 Command Code TDINQ
CONDITION
The TIF file requested was not available for Real Time research.

Note: TDINQ will perform a security check of the user profile to determine if the user is restricted for access to IMF-only or accounts. If the user profile and the input request are not consistent, one of the following error messages will be generated:
The user is profiled for access to BMF accounts only. The input account is not BMF.
